# Auth
## User
### Register user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "hello2@test.com",
  "password": "test123",
  "role": "ORGANIZER"
}

### Login user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "hello@test.com",
  "password": "test123"
}

# Events
## Create
### Create Event - success
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Imagine Dragons",
  "description": "Nouvelle description",
  "startDate": "2031-01-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "venueId": "venue-99",
  "capacity": 150,
  "price": 25,
  "organizerId": "user-1",
  "categoryId": "cat-1",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/new-image.jpg"
}

### Create Event - missing title
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "Sans titre",
  "startDate": "2030-01-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "venueId": "venue-1",
  "capacity": 100,
  "price": 20,
  "organizerId": "user-1",
  "categoryId": "cat-1"
}

### Create Event - past date
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Event passé",
  "description": "Date invalide",
  "startDate": "2020-01-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "venueId": "venue-1",
  "capacity": 100,
  "price": 20,
  "organizerId": "user-1",
  "categoryId": "cat-1"
}

## Get
### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get event by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## Update
### Update event (PUT) - remplace <ID>
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Imagine Dragons",
  "description": "Mise à jour",
  "startDate": "2031-01-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "venueId": "venue-99",
  "capacity": 150,
  "price": 25,
  "organizerId": "user-1",
  "categoryId": "cat-1",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/new-image.jpg"
}

## Delete
### Delete event (DELETE) - supprime <ID>
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# A2F / OTP
## 1) Récupérer le QR Code (auth requis)
### Get QRCode (success)
GET {{a2fUrl}}/qrcode
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 2) Activer la 2FA (auth requis + rate limit 4/min)
# ⚠️ Remplace "DJBVEA3QGMZHY4ZE" par le secret reçu au step 1
# ⚠️ Remplace "123456" par le code affiché dans ton appli OTP
### Enable A2F (success)
POST {{a2fUrl}}/enable
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "secret": "DJBVEA3QGMZHY4ZE",
  "code": "123456"
}

### Enable A2F - missing fields
POST {{a2fUrl}}/enable
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "secret": "",
  "code": ""
}

### Enable A2F - invalid code
POST {{a2fUrl}}/enable
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "secret": "SECRET_FROM_QRCODE",
  "code": "000000"
}

## 3) Tester le rate limit
# Lance cette requête 5 fois en moins d'une minute : la 5e doit renvoyer 429
### Enable A2F - rate limit test
POST {{a2fUrl}}/enable
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "secret": "SECRET_FROM_QRCODE",
  "code": "123456"
}